<p>We've got a <code>User</code>, we've got a <code>Genus</code>... so how can we smash them together? Well,
in <code>Genus</code>, the <code>genusScientists</code> property is private. Add a new function so we can
put stuff into it: <code>public function: addGenusScientist()</code> with a <code>User</code> argument:</p>
